            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Otto Feuer</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#feuerO" start="4709.586" end="x">One of my brothers is in <a class="placename" href="#vothL490">Erie</a>, in Pennsylvania.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
