            <span class="utterance" who="#feuerO" start="4738.926" end="x">[In ecstasy] Tell him, he is a little bit ill [??] . . . tell him I love him very much, and tell him he shall . . . he shall . . . here, here [he apparently points to a part of the body] sick, you know, I want him to be, I want him to be healthy . . .</span>
